{"tid":2360933,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英美等四國發表外長聯合聲明　籲北京尊重香港人自由","createTime":"2021-01-10T08:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T11:37:20.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"86e511e47c197b1f82b419c013ac5dfe17f2a62e","tid":2360933,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T08:19:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569637-20210110.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569637-20210110.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=86d0b60e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569637-20210110.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fff357a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569637-20210110.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n五眼聯盟中的四國，發表外長聯合聲明，譴責香港特區政府早前拘捕超過50名協調及參與民主派初選人士，呼籲北京方面尊重香港人的自由。<br />\n<br />\n四國包括美國、加拿大、英國及澳洲。聲明說，很明顯香港國安法被利用作為排除不同政見及反對意見的工具，呼籲香港特區政府及北京中央政府，尊重香港人獲法律保障的自由及權利，而不會擔心被捕及被扣留。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，美國國務卿蓬佩奧說，華盛頓方面可能制裁牽涉香港今次拘捕行動的人。"},{"pid":"e1d1125f72eb7dc5b8576bcdc7371c3018c61475","tid":2360933,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T08:20:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>四國包括美國、加拿大、英國及澳洲。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n羊仔國失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e43cc2c1babf81b8b0134256533dfe1a619e56","tid":2360933,"uid":129676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T08:33:14.000Z","msg":"我要自由呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf56f05fefbe0debb827f0d02b68fd306e58401","tid":2360933,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T10:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=